    "description": "BRAVE ADVENTURER - The story of a vagabond who travels through Middle-earth and is the victim of an attack by bandits, resulting in serious injury.<br>You enter the world of demons through the use of dark magic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387030/extras/ca8d1f5231844c9f34efbab1316246b2.poster.avif?t=1682792534\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387030/extras/ca8d1f5231844c9f34efbab1316246b2.webm?t=1682792534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387030/extras/ca8d1f5231844c9f34efbab1316246b2.mp4?t=1682792534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>BRAVE ADVENTURER - This is a 2D platform game where you have to play as a character and bypass traps and obstacles to get to a certain goal. You can choose from many levels with different features and mechanics.<br><br>But existence in this world turned out to be much more dangerous and threatening to your life than on the surface.<br>You must do everything possible to get out of there and return to your world.<br>You have to fight sinister demons, overcome difficulties and solve puzzles to find a way out of this nightmare.<br>The only way to survive and return home is to use all your skills and knowledge, and not lose hope of salvation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387030/extras/f5b24f7eb3c99d6ce802266f8877f524.poster.avif?t=1682792534\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387030/extras/f5b24f7eb3c99d6ce802266f8877f524.webm?t=1682792534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamsta